rl_meta":{"origin":33929,"position":0},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Debates: Arguing in religion breeds hate, bad will","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Rabia\u2019 ibn Sulayman reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cArguing about the religion hardens the heart and produces resentment.\u201d And Al-Shafi'i said, \"I never debated anyone but with sincere good will.\" Source: Siyar A'la\u0304m al-Nubala\u0304' 10\/28 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0639 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0633\u064f\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0650\u064a\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34348,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/08\/04\/shafii-on-too-much-debate\/","url_meta":{"origin":33929,"position":1},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Debate: Too much debating belittles status of knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 4, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn \u2018Abd al-Hakam reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cAmong the degradation of knowledge is that you debate everyone who debates you, or you argue with everyone who argues with you.\u201d And he said, \u201cKnowledge is ignorance to the people of ignorance, just as ignorance is ignorance\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26866,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/11\/17\/shafii-desire-no-praise\/","url_meta":{"origin":33929,"position":2},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Knowledge: I desire no praise or credit for teaching","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 17, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Hatim reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI never debated anyone and loved for him to be wrong. There is no knowledge in my heart but that I wish everyone could have it and attribute none of it to me.\u201d Source: A\u0304da\u0304b al-Sha\u0304fi\u2019i\u0304 wa Mana\u0304qibuh\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3626,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/11\/best-provision-fear-of-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33929,"position":3},"title":"Shafi&#8217;i on Provisions: Best provision is fear of Allah, worst is aggression","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bayhaqi reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe most beneficial of provisions is the fear of Allah, and the most harmful of provisions is aggression.\u201d Source: al-Madkhal ila\u0304 al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 401 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0647\u0642\u064a \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0639\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0630\u064e\u0651\u062e\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u064e\u0651\u0642\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0649 \u0648\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0636\u064e\u0631\u064f\u0651\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064f\u062f\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064f 401 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062f\u062e\u0644 \u0625\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0646\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27542,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/13\/best-answer-fool-silence\/","url_meta":{"origin":33929,"position":4},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Debate: Best answer to a fool is silence","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Imam al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah be pleased with him, said in his poetry, \u201cIf a fool speaks to you, do not answer him, for the best answer is silence. If you speak to him, you have delighted him. If you leave him, he nearly dies in anguish.\u201d Source: Di\u0304wa\u0304n al-Ima\u0304m al-Sha\u0304fi\u2019i\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26012,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/04\/only-knowledge-benefit\/","url_meta":{"origin":33929,"position":5},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Knowledge: It is only knowledge if it benefits you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 4, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"A